{
    "_comment": "Sparse Structure VAE Stage1-only finetune on Fusion360 voxelized BRep",
    "_description": "Finetune encoder + decoder_stage1 from stable_v2 to improve occupancy and semantic stage1 metrics.",
    "models": {
